A method for issuing community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances as digital certificates, comprising the steps of:
 Providing a verifiable credential wallet on a blockchain, wherein said wallet is used to store and manage digital credentials;
 Generating a machine learning model based on a dataset of community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances;
 Utilizing said machine learning model to authenticate and issue digital credentials for community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances;
 Allowing users to pay for said digital credentials using a digital wallet on a blockchain;
 Storing said digital credentials and payment transactions on said blockchain.
 An innovative method for issuing community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances as digital certificates, comprising the steps of:
 Utilizing verifiable credential technology to issue digital credentials for community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances;
 Using a blockchain to store and manage said digital credentials and payment transactions;
 Generating a machine learning model based on a dataset of community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances;
 Authenticating and issuing digital credentials for community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances using said machine learning model;
 Allowing users to pay for said digital credentials using a digital wallet on a blockchain;
 Storing said digital credentials and payment transactions on said blockchain.
